---
interface Props {
  kicker: string
  title: string
  summary: string
}

const { kicker, title, summary } = Astro.props
---

<section class="relative py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-8 h-64 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500/10 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-blue-200 uppercase">{kicker}</p>
      <h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl font-pj">{title}</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">{summary}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]">
      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-[#121720] p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-black/20">
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-200 uppercase">Reliability</p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold text-white">99.98%</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-gray-300">Healthy deployments, clear rollback paths, and visible edge metrics.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-200 uppercase">Coverage</p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold text-white">9 locales</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-gray-300">The reproduction keeps localized route expansion because the real bug appears in that setup.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 p-6 md:col-span-2">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-gray-400 uppercase">Audit trail</p>
            <div class="mt-5 space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-white">Build output inspected</p>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-gray-300">The real bug is in the emitted route manifest, not just in preview runtime behavior.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-violet-400"></span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-white">Route graph aligned</p>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-gray-300">Flat marketing pages are part of the reproduction because the landing repo is dominated by them.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-white">Docs remain separate</p>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-gray-300">Until the repro leaks the Starlight chunk onto these routes, it is still missing part of the trigger.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-linear-to-br from-[#161d27] to-[#0f141b] p-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-400 uppercase">Control plane</p>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-5">
          <div class="status-row rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 px-5 py-4">
            <span class="text-gray-200">Preview manifest</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-500/15 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-blue-200">Inspect</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-row rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 px-5 py-4">
            <span class="text-gray-200">Website routes</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-500/15 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-emerald-200">Flattened</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-row rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 px-5 py-4">
            <span class="text-gray-200">Docs routes</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-violet-500/15 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-violet-200">Starlight</span>
          </div>
          <div class="status-row rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 px-5 py-4">
            <span class="text-gray-200">Cloudflare adapter</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-amber-500/15 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-amber-200">Enabled</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .status-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
</style>
